---
const title = "openclaw40+使用指南";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding: 16px 40px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 140px 20px 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #f5f5f7 100%);
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0071e3 0%, #42a5f 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .tagline {
            font-size: 21px;
            color: #86868b;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: #0071e3;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 24px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background: #0077ed;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,113,227,0.25);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f5f5f7;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #e8e8ed;
        }
        
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            border: 1px solid #d2d2d7;
        }
        
        .card h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .card p {
            color: #86868b;
        }
        
        .nav {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        .nav h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        
        .nav-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
        }
        
        .nav-card {
            display: block;
            padding: 24px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            border: 1px solid #d2d2d7;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .nav-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }
        
        .nav-card h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .nav-card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #86868b;
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            color: #86868b;
            border-top: 1px solid #d2d2d7;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1>openclaw40+使用指南</h1>
    </header>
    
    <section class="hero">
        <h1>从零开始，轻松掌握<br><span class="gradient">OpenClaw AI 助理</span></h1>
        <p class="tagline">本站专为40岁以上完全不懂程序是什么的人群如何使用openclaw而建</p>
        <a href="#start" class="btn">开始阅读</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw" class="btn btn-secondary">查看 GitHub</a>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🤖 私有化部署</h3>
            <p>数据完全存储在你自己的服务器上，隐私安全无忧</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>💬 多平台接入</h3>
            <p>支持 Telegram、Discord、飞书、钉钉等平台</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🧩 丰富技能生态</h3>
            <p>5000+ 社区技能，一键安装即用</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="nav" id="start">
        <h2>快速导航</h2>
        <div class="nav-grid">
            <a href="/install" class="nav-card">
                <h3>📦 安装篇</h3>
                <p>环境准备、快速安装、配置指南</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/usage" class="nav-card">
                <h3>💡 使用篇</h3>
                <p>基础操作、技能安装、通道配置</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/faq" class="nav-card">
                <h3>❓ FAQ</h3>
                <p>常见问题、错误排查</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/resources" class="nav-card">
                <h3>📚 资源推荐</h3>
                <p>精选技能、视频教程</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <p>Made with ❤️ by openclaw40+ 社区</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
